{"tid":2040123,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港驚現罕有「地震魚」！一般棲息於深海 或成香港出現地震預兆？","createTime":"2020-05-28T11:13:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T11:55:59.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"8c0669206cf26bb7754ad19a7f7fb5d0fbc9e4f6","tid":2040123,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T11:13:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://holiday.presslogic.com/article/183440/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%A9%9A%E7%8F%BE%E7%BD%95%E6%9C%89-%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87%E9%AD%9A-%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E6%A3%B2%E6%81%AF%E6%96%BC%E6%B7%B1%E6%B5%B7-%E6%88%96%E6%88%90%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%87%BA%E7%8F%BE%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87%E9%A0%90%E5%85%86\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholiday.presslogic.com%2Farticle%2F183440%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%25A9%259A%25E7%258F%25BE%25E7%25BD%2595%25E6%259C%2589-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%259C%2587%25E9%25AD%259A-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%2588%25AC%25E6%25A3%25B2%25E6%2581%25AF%25E6%2596%25BC%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E6%25B5%25B7-%25E6%2588%2596%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%259C%2587%25E9%25A0%2590%25E5%2585%2586&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu5tjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=95f20d32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://holiday.presslogic.com/article/183440/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%A9%9A%E7%8F%BE%E7%BD%95%E6%9C%89-%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87%E9%AD%9A-%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E6%A3%B2%E6%81%AF%E6%96%BC%E6%B7%B1%E6%B5%B7-%E6%88%96%E6%88%90%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%87%BA%E7%8F%BE%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87%E9%A0%90%E5%85%86</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PKKWBFM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPKKWBFM.jpg&h=bddaf038&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b6a08c1729fd427efec23234740699db7ba2c98","tid":2040123,"uid":55122,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T11:14:51.000Z","msg":"如果震得成 <br />\n我直播切JJ塞落我屎眼到"},{"pid":"9586b612468752848d8ddfbe9ef21509ac5ae2c7","tid":2040123,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T11:14:53.000Z","msg":"By<br />\nJennifer<br />\non<br />\n28 May 2020<br />\nDigital Editor<br />\n<br />\n最近有網民喺香港發現有俗稱「地震魚」嘅皇帶魚，引發香港或會出現地震嘅憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n有玩開《動物森友會》嘅朋友仔應該都有釣過皇帶魚，皇帶魚身體呈扁平狀，身長最高可達11米。<br />\n<br />\n最近有網民喺香港發現有俗稱「地震魚」嘅皇帶魚，引發香港或會出現地震嘅憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n有玩開《動物森友會》嘅朋友仔應該都有釣過皇帶魚，皇帶魚身體呈扁平狀，身長最高可達11米。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n皇帶魚一般棲息於200至1,000米深海帶，由於外形獨特，有唔少傳說。<br />\n<br />\n日本人認為皇帶魚係「龍宮使者」，而且因為皇帶魚向來棲息於深海，所以認為只有板塊移動先會令佢出現喺淺水區。<br />\n<br />\n因此皇帶魚出現就被認為係預示會發生大地震，又被稱為「地震魚」。<br />\n<br />\n皇帶魚出現就被認為係預示會發生大地震，又被稱為「地震魚」<br />\nPhoto from 魚津水族館<br />\n皇帶魚出現就被認為係預示會發生大地震，又被稱為「地震魚」<br />\n最近有網民喺香港南丫島海灘上發現「地震魚」嘅屍體，而該皇帶魚屍體已乾透發白，相信已被沖上岸好幾日。"},{"pid":"bc49d0aa228d1294c4d99a6ea9168cae4339fa8e","tid":2040123,"uid":38646,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"4b6a08c1729fd427efec23234740699db7ba2c98","tid":2040123,"uid":55122,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T11:14:51.000Z","msg":"如果震得成 <br />\n我直播切JJ塞落我屎眼到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T11:16:28.000Z","msg":"冇人想睇牙籤塞屎眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3037b6a80ddb641045ab0938fcfc85f42c52b136","tid":2040123,"uid":12597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T11:16:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"397488cae7c32144ae842e448275dab57994bbd1","tid":2040123,"uid":65638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T11:17:45.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成日都有架啦，d 人係咪搵來講？"},{"pid":"62c2952dd010fecf5ca003c28aba57882d1291f8","tid":2040123,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T11:17:52.000Z","msg":"咁撚長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03da3a327a99caf2ef7be1cb1e9edd7ae667d85c","tid":2040123,"uid":76753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1